# Episodic memory runtime artifacts — per-snapshot JSON files written by
# the synthesis/futurist hooks on every cycle. The aggregated jsonl files
# (episodes.jsonl, lessons.jsonl) ARE tracked because they hold the seeded
# baselines + accumulated graduated knowledge. The candidates/ dir is
# pure staging — entries either graduate (into lessons.jsonl) or get
# rejected, so the dir itself doesn't need to be in git.
.agent/memory/episodic/synthesis_*.json
.agent/memory/episodic/prediction_*.json
.agent/memory/episodic/trade_*.json
.agent/memory/episodic/signal_*.json
.agent/memory/candidates/

